data.description: This Beautiful Home is nestled on a .60 acre Corner level lot and features: 3 Bedrooms 2.5 bathrooms, Beautiful large covered front porch to enjoy your morning coffee or the sunset of the evenings. Hardwood and laminated flooring. White kitchen cabinets with beautiful Granite Countertop. The enclosed back porch can very easily be turned into additional living space if needed. Beautiful level fenced private back yard. In Addition this home has a workshop with additional parking space and a working well for plants or any other house shores. Very convenient to Hwy 27, only 2 miles to Hwy 140. Very convenient to Calhoun and I-75, Hurry call and schedule a showing today !!
